---
title: Library of JDRanpariya
description: "Books, lectures, and papers that shaped my thinking — curated notes and reflections on what I've been reading."
layout: layouts/base
section: "library"
---

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-14 md:py-24 flex flex-col gap-16">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="text-center space-y-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-accent">Library</h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Books, lectures, and papers that changed how I think. Notes inside.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Header for books -->
  <div class="text-center space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-accent">Books</h2>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      What I'm reading and what stuck. Notes inside each.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Books -->
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8">
      {% for book in collections.books %}
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <!-- Cover -->
          <a href="{{ book.url }}">
            {% image book.data.cover, book.data.title, "rounded-lg mb-3 w-full object-cover aspect-[2/3] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition" %}
          </a>

          <!-- Title & Author -->
          <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-serif font-medium leading-snug">
            {{ book.data.title }}
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">{{ book.data.author }}</p>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-2">
      <a
        href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/161877825-jay"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-sm text-muted hover:text-accent transition-colors"
      >
        Full reading list on Goodreads →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Header for lectures -->
  <div class="text-center space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-accent">Lectures</h2>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      These are my absolute favorite lectures that have completely blown me away! if you see their
      photo, that's me saying "this person is pure genius and I'm practically bursting to share them
      with you."
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Lectures -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    {% for lecture in collections.lectures %}
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <!-- Cover -->
        <a href="{{ lecture.url }}">
          {% image lecture.data.cover, lecture.data.title, "rounded-lg mb-3 w-full h-56 object-cover shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition" %}
        </a>

        <!-- Title & Author -->
        <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-serif font-medium leading-snug">
          {{ lecture.data.title }}
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted">{{ lecture.data.author }}</p>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <!-- Papers -->
  <div class="text-center space-y-8">
    <h2 class="text-5xl text-center md:text-6xl font-serif text-accent">Favorite Papers</h2>
    <p class="font-serif text-lg text-secondary text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      The ones I keep coming back to.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    {% for paper in collections.papers %}
      <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-surface shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <!-- Title (clickable) -->
        <a
          href="{{ paper.data.link }}"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="block text-base md:text-lg font-serif font-medium text-accent hover:underline leading-snug"
        >
          {{ paper.data.title }}
        </a>

        <!-- Author / Metadata -->
        <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-1">{{ paper.data.author }}</p>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
